---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Catering & Private Chef — Moulin à Rêves" description="Breakfast delivery, dinner service, and private chef weekends at Moulin à Rêves. Let someone else do the cooking while you enjoy the French countryside.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero" style="height: 60vh;">
    <div class="hero__image">
      <img src="/images/catering-table.webp" alt="Long dinner table set beneath garden trees at golden hour at Moulin à Rêves, Barbizon" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero__content">
      <span class="hero__eyebrow">Moulin à Rêves</span>
      <h1 class="hero__title" data-i18n="catering.hero.title">Catering</h1>
      <p class="hero__tagline" data-i18n="catering.hero.tagline">From breakfast at your door to a private chef for the weekend.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .hero__eyebrow {
      display: block;
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 0.6875rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.28em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      text-shadow: 0 1px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
      padding-left: 0.28em;
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container--narrow text-center fade-in">
      <h2 data-i18n="catering.intro.heading">Let Someone Else Cook</h2>
      <p data-i18n="catering.intro.text" style="margin-top: 24px;">
        You're on holiday. The kitchen is stocked, the markets are close, and cooking with fresh ingredients is part of the joy. But some mornings, you'd rather find a basket of warm croissants at the door. And some evenings, you'd rather sit down to a table already set, a meal already made, a bottle already opened. That's what this is for.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Breakfast -->
  <section class="fade-in">
    <div class="split">
      <div class="split__image">
        <img src="/images/outdoor-dining.webp" alt="Fresh breakfast basket with croissants and local jam delivered to your door at Moulin à Rêves" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="split__body">
        <span class="eyebrow">Morning</span>
        <h2 data-i18n="catering.breakfast.heading">Breakfast Delivery</h2>
        <p data-i18n="catering.breakfast.p1">
          Each morning, a basket arrives at your door before you've finished your first coffee. Inside: croissants from the boulangerie in Barbizon, a fresh baguette, local butter and confiture, seasonal fruit, yoghurt, and juice. If you have dietary needs or preferences, let us know — everything is prepared to order.
        </p>
        <p data-i18n="catering.breakfast.p2">
          You'll take it to the terrace, or the kitchen table, or the garden — wherever your morning happens to lead. It's the simplest thing, and it changes the whole rhythm of the day.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Dinner Service -->
  <section class="fade-in">
    <div class="split split--reverse">
      <div class="split__body">
        <span class="eyebrow">Evening</span>
        <h2 data-i18n="catering.dinner.heading">Dinner Service</h2>
        <p data-i18n="catering.dinner.p1">
          On the evenings you'd rather not cook, our local chef prepares a three-course meal and delivers it to your kitchen — still warm, beautifully presented, ready to plate. The menus change with the season: a cold cucumber soup in July, a duck confit with roasted figs in October, a tarte tatin made with apples from the garden's own tree.
        </p>
        <p data-i18n="catering.dinner.p2">
          You set the table, open the wine, and take all the credit. The dishes are collected the next morning with the breakfast delivery.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="split__image">
        <img src="/images/gazebo-dining.webp" alt="Beautifully plated seasonal dinner under the gazebo at Moulin à Rêves, France" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Special Occasions -->
  <section class="fade-in">
    <div class="split">
      <div class="split__image">
        <img src="/images/catering-table.webp" alt="Special occasion dinner in the garden with candles and flowers at Moulin à Rêves" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="split__body">
        <span class="eyebrow">Celebrations</span>
        <h2 data-i18n="catering.special.heading">Special Occasions</h2>
        <p data-i18n="catering.special.p1">
          A birthday. An anniversary. The last night of a reunion when everyone is finally, fully relaxed. For these evenings, we arrange something more: a multi-course menu designed around your preferences, table settings, flowers, candles in the garden. The chef cooks on-site while you enjoy apéritifs on the lawn, and the meal unfolds at whatever pace the evening demands.
        </p>
        <p data-i18n="catering.special.p2">
          Tell us the occasion, the number of guests, and any dietary requirements, and we'll put together a proposal.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Private Chef -->
  <section class="fade-in">
    <div class="split split--reverse">
      <div class="split__body">
        <span class="eyebrow">Full Service</span>
        <h2 data-i18n="catering.chef.heading">Private Chef Weekends</h2>
        <p data-i18n="catering.chef.p1">
          For groups who want to hand over the kitchen entirely, we arrange a private chef for the duration of your stay. They'll shop at the morning markets, cook breakfast and dinner each day, and adapt the menus to your group — vegan guests, children's meals, a birthday cake at the end.
        </p>
        <p data-i18n="catering.chef.p2">
          Your chef knows the local producers, the seasonal ingredients, and the way a meal should feel when you're eating it outdoors in the French countryside: generous, unhurried, built around what's good right now.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="split__image">
        <img src="/images/outdoor-dining.webp" alt="Outdoor dining prepared by private chef at Moulin à Rêves countryside compound" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonial -->
  <section class="section section--stone">
    <div class="container text-center fade-in">
      <blockquote class="testimonial" data-i18n="catering.testimonial">
        "We had the private chef for four nights and it transformed the trip. Every meal was an event. The duck with cherry sauce on the last evening — I still think about it."
      </blockquote>
      <p class="testimonial__attribution" data-i18n="catering.testimonial.attribution">— Anna, July 2025</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="hero" style="height: 45vh; min-height: 350px;">
    <div class="hero__image">
      <img src="/images/catering-table.webp" alt="Dinner table in the garden at Moulin à Rêves" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero__content">
      <h2 class="hero__title" data-i18n="catering.cta.heading" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);">Hungry?</h2>
      <p class="hero__tagline" data-i18n="catering.cta.text">Tell us what you'd like and we'll put together a catering proposal for your stay. All pricing is available on inquiry.</p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--white" data-i18n="catering.cta.button">Inquire About Catering</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
